<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="account-n">account <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ə'kaʊnt/    美 /əˈkaʊnt/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[常用复数] 账；账目：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an account book 
账本；账簿</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He takes care of the business and his wife keeps the accounts. 
他打理生意，他太太则负责记账。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>账户；账号：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>open / close an account</strong>
开/销户</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>have an account at / with a bank</strong>
在银行开户</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>create an e-mail account 
创建电子邮件账户</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the WeChat official / public account
微信公众号</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My father helped me set up <strong>a bank account</strong>. 
我爸爸帮我开了个银行账户。</p><footer>2010 辽宁</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>叙述；报道；描写：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an <strong>eye-witness account of</strong> a murder
目击者对一起谋杀的描述</p><footer>人教⑥ – 5</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>While this book tells the stories of famous people in history, it also <strong>gives an account of</strong> the lives of lesserknown individuals.
这本书在讲述历史名人的故事的同时，还讲述不太出名的人的生活。</p><footer>2017 江苏改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="on-account-of">on account of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>因为；由于 (because of)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She was absent from school on account of illness.
她因病没有去学校。</p></div>

<h3 id="on-no-account">on no account</h3>
<p>1.<strong>决不；绝对不：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The professor warned the students that on no account should they use mobile phones in his class.
教授警告学生，在他的课上绝对不能用手机。</p><footer>2019 天津</footer></div>

<p>注: on no account置于句首，其所在的句子要用倒装语序。  </p>
<h3 id="take-account-of-take-into-account">take account of / take ... into account</h3>
<p>1.<strong>考虑到；把……考虑进去：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The company takes account of environmental issues wherever possible. 
只要有可能，这家公司都会考虑到环境问题。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>One must take the audience into account when making speeches. 
人们在演讲时必须要考虑听众。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (开了个银行账户) after I made $1,000 by doing a part-time job during the summer vacation.  （2011 天津改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. opened/set up a bank account  </p></div>